---
const personalImageAlt = 'Landing Fitness Pro'

import MailIcon from '@/icons/Mail.astro'
import SocialPill from './SocialPill.astro'
---

<div class='flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center max-w-4xl'>
    <div class='flex justify-center gap-4 mb-4'>
        <img
            class='rounded-full shadow-lg size-16'
            src='/Logo.jpeg'
            alt={personalImageAlt}
        />
    </div>
    <h1
        class='text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl dark:text-white text-shadow'
    >
        Landing Page Profesional
    </h1>
    <p
        class='mt-6 text-2xl text-gray-800 dark:[&>strong]:text-green-400 [&>strong]:text-green-500 [&>strong]:font-semibold dark:text-gray-300'
    >
        Especializados en hacer de la <strong>visita una conversión.</strong>
    </p>
    <p
        class='mt-6 text-xl text-gray-800 dark:[&>strong]:text-green-400 [&>strong]:text-green-500 [&>strong]:font-semibold dark:text-gray-300'
    >
        Desarrollamos páginas web para abogados, contadores y gestores,
        <strong>potenciando</strong>
        su marca personal e <strong>incrementando</strong> su visibilidad.
    </p>
    <nav class='flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-8'>
        <span class='relative inline-flex overflow-hidden rounded-full p-[1px]'>
            <span
                class='absolute inset-[-1000%] animate-[spin_2s_linear_infinite] bg-[conic-gradient(from_90deg_at_50%_50%,#E45151_0%,#552121_50%,#E45151_100%)]'
            ></span>
            <div
                class='inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full text-sm text-green-800 bg-green-100 rounded-full cursor-pointer dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-white/80 backdrop-blur-3xl whitespace-nowrap'
            >
                <SocialPill href='#calendly'>
                    <MailIcon class='size-6' />
                    Agendar reunión
                </SocialPill>
            </div>
        </span>
    </nav>
</div>

<style>
    .text-shadow {
        text-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgb(67, 214, 14);
    }
</style>
